<div class="title">Ultimate Zen State</div>
<div class="substance">2C-E & Cannabis</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=hallucinagent&Exact=1">hallucinagent</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; hallucinagent. "Ultimate Zen State: An Experience with 2C-E & Cannabis (exp96910)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Nov 25, 2012. erowid.org/exp/96910</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
